20around%20you%20is%20living%20a%20completely%20different%20life.%20That's%20the%20hardest%20part%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22833703ed-a996-4563-b6cf-9a88ae8655fd%5C%22%3EA%20day%20in%20my%20life%20as%20a%20student%20founder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-founder-single-mother-day-in-the-life-schedule-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20start%20my%20day%20%3C%2Fa%3Earound%208%20a.m.%2C%20checking%20emails%2C%20Slack%2C%20and%20work%20updates.%20Then%20I%20head%20to%20campus%20and%20attend%20classes%2C%20mostly%20for%20attendance.%20I%20usually%20work%20during%20lectures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20avoid%20scheduling%20calls%20during%20class%20hours%2C%20but%20things%20often%20overlap.%20Sometimes%20I%20have%20to%20leave%20mid-class%20or%20skip%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20school%2C%20I%20move%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-embracing-remote-work-amid-rto-push-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20a%20coworking%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20and%20continue%20working%20and%20taking%20calls%20until%20around%207%20to%208%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20get%20home%2C%20I%20start%20working%20on%20our%20US-based%20accounts%20until%201%20to%202%20a.m.%20because%20of%20the%20time%20zone%20difference.%20I%20usually%20use%20the%20time%20on%20weekends%20to%20focus%20on%20Genta's%20internal%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20I%20try%20to%20disconnect%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20by%20taking%20bike%20rides%20outside%20the%20city%2C%20swimming%2C%20or%20catching%20up%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20that%20isn't%20work%20or%20university-related.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20this%20way%20for%20almost%20a%20year%20hasn't%20been%20easy%2C%20but%20I've%20gotten%20used%20to%20it%2C%20and%20I've%20grown%20to%20love%20the%20rhythm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b062fb8d-a2ff-422b-b0e4-a5b950c73dbd%5C%22%3EAge%20shouldn't%20stop%20you%20from%20being%20a%20founder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20buy%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturbo-ai-notetaking-app-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eage%20is%20a%20barrier%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20starting%20a%20company.%20But%20it%20can%20be%20a%20problem%2C%20especially%20when%20working%20with%20bigger%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20clients%20that%20I%20could%20have%20done%20so%20much%20for%2C%20but%20the%20main%20reason%20we%20didn't%20proceed%20is%20because%20of%20how%20young%20I%20was%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-pitch-decks-startup-young-founders-raising-millions-ai-yc-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20new%20the%20company%20was%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%2C%20especially%20AI%2C%20is%20such%20a%20new%20technology.%20It%20needs%20people%20who%20can%20move%2C%20learn%2C%20and%20adapt%20fast%2C%20which%20you%20usually%20see%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-founders-younger-technical-vcs-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20younger%20generation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20clients%20actually%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20me.%20They%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20young%2C%20he%20doesn't%20have%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20they%20try%20to%20get%20more%20work%20for%20free%2C%20or%20they%20try%20to%20cut%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20disrespectful%20to%20do%20purely%20based%20on%20age.%20I%20try%20to%20prove%20myself%20and%20gain%20that%20respect%20with%20work%2C%20focusing%20on%20getting%20the%20ROI.%20Then%20they%20don't%20just%20respect%20you%2C%20but%20they%20want%20to%20work%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20trickiest%20things%20for%20me%20is%20being%20a%20manager.%20It's%20a%20new%20experience%2C%20and%20I%20always%20try%20to%20be%20as%20nice%20and%20as%20chill%20as%20possible%20with%20my%20team.%20I%20hate%20micromanaging%20and%20having%20to%20be%20bossy%2C%20but%20I%20expect%20a%20lot%20from%20my%2016-member%20team%2C%20which%20is%20spread%20across%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20I%20experience%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realize%20that%20there's%20still%20much%20I%20need%20to%20work%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollege%20students%20should%20never%20wait%20until%20something%20happens%20or%20until%20they%20reach%20a%20certain%20level%20to%20start.%20Do%20now%2C%20learn%20later.%20You'll%20only%20figure%20it%20out%20once%20you%20start.%20You%20should%20not%20know%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20being%20a%20young%20AI%20founder%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acmlee%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ecmlee%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40cmlee.81.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-university-ai-founder-startup-losing-student-life-komy-genta-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764549886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69141f7862a04500b31637d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-university-ai-founder-startup-losing-student-life-komy-genta-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2022-year-old%20cybersecurity%20student%20shares%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20build%20an%20AI%20startup%20in%20university%2C%20and%20why%20being%20a%20young%20founder%20can%20feel%20lonely.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmlee%40insider.com%20(Lee%20Chong%20Ming)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-university-ai-founder-startup-losing-student-life-komy-genta-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Outdoor%20Boys%20star%20Luke%20Nichol